    <generalfeedback format="moodle_auto_format">
				<text><![CDATA[In each case we apply the binomial theorem, which can be stated as \[(a+b)^n =\sum_{i=0}^n \binom{n}{i}a^ib^{n-i}\] where \(\displaystyle{\binom{n}{i}=\dfrac{n!}{(n-i)!i!}}\).

<br><br><br><ol class="HELM_parts">

    <li>
        <p>\(({@aa@}+x)^{{@ai@}}={@ta1@}\)<br></p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <p>\( (a+b)^{{@bi@}}={@ta2@}\) <br></p>
    </li>
</ol>
<ol class="HELM_parts">

</ol>]]></text>
